{"tid":1432071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【運動次要效用】 清算藥房金舖","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:18:31.000Z","uid":299171,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7da73262d07e2c094d39bfd35165326347cb18","tid":1432071,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JTYR3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JTYR3q.jpg&h=7751f5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>圖片轉自FB</strong><br />\n是日海港城，無蝗蟲無蝗語，周圍嘅都係講人話嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n運動嚟到呢個位可能有人會開始灰心，問自己咁做有咩用。唔可以咁。<br />\n<br />\n而家就唔講主要目標，講次要效用。暴政固然係香港人第一敵人，但擾民嘅仲有每日拖著篋橫衝直撞，蝗未到聲先到嘅蝗蟲，以及視佢哋為皇帝嘅親蝗商鋪。<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時開始，湧現咗一堆靠支那蟲搵食嘅親蝗舖，每當香港人做正確嘅事，呢對親蝗舖就會以「搞亂香港經濟」為口號抹黑香港人，事實上所謂嘅「搞亂香港經濟」只係影響緊呢啲單一依賴蝗蟲衛生嘅親蝗舖，寄生於蝗蟲嘅寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲親蝗舖必須清算。 即使你對運動開始灰心，都唔可以抹殺運動帶嚟嘅實則效用 &mdash;&mdash; 餓撚死呢班親蝗狗。"},{"pid":"5f1069eb5b5c355ae16e04222d9f09b3ef074349","tid":1432071,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"餓撚死呢班親蝗狗"},{"pid":"96374f53940781212ef34f05bc94d790638348a1","tid":1432071,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"獻世派講嘅「還香港清淨」<br />\n達到了，無蝗蟲自然清淨"},{"pid":"13ecbd414ebaaf857de9f60f129e34c3ebd54860","tid":1432071,"uid":88029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0bfd004ec415330aba2795d4371aab0f908e954","tid":1432071,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港! 時代革命!</span></span>"},{"pid":"e35577df3ec836a97c577e11b4f4874fb15f51e9","tid":1432071,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"包賺嫁?"},{"pid":"6078684d0c2e3a43da06c2b0c709715fa3bb534f","tid":1432071,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">清算金舖藥房<br />\n變相全港驅蝗</span></span></strong>"}]}